title: Measles
note: Note: CDC data from 2003-2012 comes from its Summary of Notifiable Diseases, which publishes yearly rather than weekly and counts confirmed cases as opposed to provisional ones.

title: Pertussis (Whooping Cough)
note: Note: The CDC did not report any weekly, state level data for pertussis between 1955 and 1974. The vaccine was introduced in 1914.

title: Smallpox
note: Note: The vaccine for smallpox was introduced in 1800.
